snippet.title: Rob Deniel - Ikaw Sana (Performance Video)
snippet.description:
#robdeniel #ikawsana #vicormusic
Rob Deniel breathes fresh life into Ogie Alcasid’s timeless hit “Ikaw Sana” with his signature blend of powerful vocals and retro-pop sensibilities. While the original is a heartfelt ballad of longing and unspoken love, Rob’s version wraps it in a youthful glow layered with mellow instrumentation. With this track, Rob Deniel proves that great love songs never age – they simply find fresh voices to tell their story. 

Rob Deniel revitalizes an enduring Ogie Alcasid classic. See his passionate performance of "Ikaw Sana" unvarnished, sentimental, and breathtaking.

Published by Viva Music Publishing, Inc.

snippet.title: Marvel Animation's Marvel Zombies - Official Teaser Trailer #2 (2025) Elizabeth Olsen, Paul Rudd
snippet.description:
Don't miss the Teaser Trailer #2 for Marvel Animation’s Marvel Zombies, an animated horror installment to the Marvel Cinematic Universe distributed by Marvel Studios. This series re-contextualizes the Marvel Universe as Earth's mightiest heroes go head-to-head against a zombie outbreak, turning even the strongest of them into undead nightmares. Marvel Animation’s Marvel Zombies will be a four-part event on September 24, streaming exclusively on Disney+.

After the Avengers are overtaken by a zombie plague, a desperate group of survivors discover the key to bringing an end to the super-powered undead, racing across a dystopian landscape and risking life and limb to save their world. 
 
Marvel Zombies stars Elizabeth Olsen, Paul Rudd, Florence Pugh, David Harbour, Tessa Thompson, Simu Liu, Awkwafina, Hailee Steinfeld, Wyatt Russell, Randall Park, Iman Vellani, Dominique Thorne, and more. The series is executive produced by Kevin Feige, Louis D’Esposito, Brad Winderbaum, Dana Vasquez-Eberhardt, Bryan Andrews, and Zeb Wells, and is produced by Danielle Costa, Carrie Wassenaar. 

Marvel Animation’s Marvel Zombies will be a four-part event on September 24, streaming exclusively on Disney+.

#IGN #Marvel #MCU
